text: Novaya Mikhaylovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Maloyazovsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 7 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 5 km from Maloyaz, 5 km from Tatarsky Maloyaz. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Novaya Mikhaylovka
